## Medications

**How do I add a medication?**
From the Health tab or any member's profile, tap "Add Medication." Enter the name, dosage, form, and schedule. Vitals HQ will send reminders at each scheduled time.

**Can I track medications for family members?**
Yes. When adding a medication, use the "For" picker at the top to choose any family member. You can also log doses and manage meds from any member's profile.

**I'm not getting medication reminders.**
Check the following: make sure notifications are enabled for Vitals HQ in your device Settings → Notifications; confirm the medication has scheduled times set (not "as needed"); and verify that the medication is marked as active.

**What is the follow-up alert?**
If you haven't confirmed a dose within 30 minutes of the scheduled time, Vitals HQ sends a second "overdue" notification as a safety net.

