## Health & Wellness

**What vitals can I track?**
Temperature, heart rate, blood pressure, SpO2, weight, and respiratory rate. If you use Apple Watch or another HealthKit-compatible device, some of these pre-fill automatically.

**How do wellness check-ins work?**
Tap "Log Wellness" to rate energy, mood, sleep quality, appetite, and pain on a simple scale. Add symptom tags, notes, or photos. Over time this builds a history you can review with your doctor.

**Does Vitals HQ connect to Apple Health?**
Yes. Vitals HQ reads heart rate, step count, and sleep data from HealthKit (with your permission) and displays them on your dashboard. Medication doses can also be written to HealthKit.

