## Family Features

**Can family members manage each other's data?**
Yes. Any member can add events, log medications, or record wellness data for any other member. A child can add a parent meeting to your calendar, and you can track your child's medications from your own device.

**How does family sync work?**
Vitals HQ uses iCloud to sync family data across devices. All members in your iCloud family group see the same data in real time. No third-party servers are involved.

**Why are some family members showing a lock icon?**
Locked members are beyond your current subscription tier's limit. Their data is fully preserved and medication reminders stay active, but editing is disabled until you upgrade.

