## Contacts

**What are member-specific contacts?**
Each family member gets a contact list tailored to their life. A toddler's list includes pediatrician, babysitter, and daycare. A working adult sees employer and coworkers. A student gets teachers, coaches, and school counselors. These build dynamically based on each person's age, role, and life situation.

**How do I add a contact?**
Go to any member's profile → Overview → "Add Contact," or navigate to their Contacts section. Choose the relationship type and fill in the details.

