## Events & Calendar

**How do I add an event?**
From the Today tab or Events tab, tap "+". Choose the event type, date, time, and which family member it's for. Set a reminder interval if you'd like an alert beforehand.

**Can I see all family events in one place?**
Yes. The Today tab shows a unified timeline across all family members. You can also filter by individual member using the name pills at the top.

