## Privacy & Data

**Where is my data stored?**
All data is stored on your device and in your private iCloud container. Vitals HQ does not use third-party servers, analytics services, or advertising networks.

**Can Vitals HQ see my health data?**
Vitals HQ only accesses the HealthKit categories you explicitly grant permission for. You can review and revoke access at any time in Settings → Privacy & Security → Health on your device.

**How do I delete my data?**
Go to Settings → Manage Profiles to remove individual members, or delete the app to remove all local data. iCloud data can be managed through iCloud settings on your device.

