## Troubleshooting

**The app is running slowly.**
Try closing and reopening the app. If the issue persists, make sure you're running the latest version from the App Store and that your device is on iOS 17 or later.

**My data isn't syncing between devices.**
Confirm that iCloud is enabled for Vitals HQ on all devices: Settings → [Your Name] → iCloud → Apps Using iCloud. Make sure all devices are signed into the same Apple ID.

**A family member's profile shows the wrong life stage.**
Go to Settings → Manage Profiles → select the member → edit their date of birth or override their life stage manually. Roles like spouse and parent always default to adult regardless of birth date.

